    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Blow up your enemies!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blasted Dice is a roguelike deckbuilder all about launching dice at your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/8a681ea9e3d6171db71721b06e888d8a.poster.avif?t=1763311823\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/8a681ea9e3d6171db71721b06e888d8a.webm?t=1763311823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/8a681ea9e3d6171db71721b06e888d8a.mp4?t=1763311823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Blasted Dice, you engage in turn-based combat, aided by the power of colorful dice and fantastical items, in order to defeat progressively stronger enemies. Form combos with your dice, gather your favorite items, and deal large amounts of damage to those blocking your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your own build!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/97c4add36bb0ec528198d5d24d73efb9.apng?t=1763311823\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/97c4add36bb0ec528198d5d24d73efb9.poster.avif?t=1763311823\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=189 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover lots of different build archetypes! From reaching insurmountable amounts of health, to hoarding all of the gold, to buying whatever die appears in the shop, or maybe just playing a big block build… There’s a build for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make a deck with your favorite dice types and gather the items that compliment your build. Find hidden items, and make your builds even better, in order to defeat those that block your path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Search for the secrets and challenge yourself!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/7ab71304552f5b560e1946774f100549.avif?t=1763311823\" width=600 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet interesting characters and hear their stories! Find out the meaning behind them, and search for what’s hidden! Maybe even let the characters aid you in combat… That’s your choice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And, if you are looking for a more difficult approach, try the game’s challenges! There’s a bunch of them, and some are even tied to secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232520/extras/bc268a5d8ae56424a8c8ec24d2205600.avif?t=1763311823\" width=600 height=244 /></span></p>",
